# Capability workspace (per CLAUDE.md §2.1 — "建议忽略")
# When a user runs `minlo init` in another project, .minlo/workspace/ is created
# there. Inside THIS repo we don't run minlo as an end-user, but if someone does
# (e.g. `minlo list` for self-test), this prevents accidentally committing the
# scratch data.
.minlo/workspace/
